+## 24. Data Flow ΓÇö Complete Chat Request
+
+Here's exactly what happens when a user sends `POST /brain/chat { "action": "send", "payload": { "chat_id": 5, "message": "How do I handle errors in Python?" } }`:
+
+```
+1. HTTP REQUEST arrives at FastAPI
+   Γöé
+2. MIDDLEWARE CHAIN (outer ΓåÆ inner):
+   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ SecurityHeadersMiddleware: adds X-Content-Type-Options, X-Frame-Options, etc.
+   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ RateLimitMiddleware: checks /brain/* ΓåÆ 30/min limit ΓåÆ PASS
+   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ RequestValidationMiddleware: scans URL for injection patterns ΓåÆ PASS
+   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ CORSMiddleware: validates origin ΓåÆ PASS
+   ΓööΓöÇΓöÇ GenesisKeyMiddleware: reads genesis_id cookie ΓåÆ sets request.state.genesis_id
+       creates Genesis Key: key_type=api_request, what="POST /brain/chat"
+   Γöé
+3. BRAIN ROUTER: POST /brain/chat
+   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Parses BrainRequest: action="send", payload={chat_id: 5, message: "..."}
+   ΓööΓöÇΓöÇ Calls _call("chat", "send", payload, _chat())
+   Γöé
+4. _call() DISPATCHER:
+   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Looks up handler: _chat()["send"] ΓåÆ send_prompt(payload)
+   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Starts timer
+   ΓööΓöÇΓöÇ Calls handler
+   Γöé
+5. send_prompt() in core/services/chat_service.py:
+   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Loads chat from DB (session.query(Chat).get(5))
+   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Loads conversation history (last 20 messages)
+   ΓööΓöÇΓöÇ Decides routing: small-talk? RAG? web search?
+   Γöé
+6. MULTI-TIER QUERY HANDLING:
+   Γöé
+   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Tier 1: VECTORDB SEARCH
+   Γöé   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ EmbeddingModel.embed_text(["How do I handle errors..."]) ΓåÆ [384-dim vector]
+   Γöé   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ QdrantVectorDB.search_vectors("documents", vector, limit=5, threshold=0.5)
+   Γöé   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Results enriched from DB (DocumentChunk ΓåÆ Document JOIN)
+   Γöé   ΓööΓöÇΓöÇ If quality > 0.6 ΓåÆ RAG response
+   Γöé
+   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Tier 2: MODEL KNOWLEDGE (if Tier 1 insufficient)
+   Γöé   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ get_llm_client() ΓåÆ OllamaAdapter (or Kimi/Opus/Qwen)
+   Γöé   ΓööΓöÇΓöÇ LLM generates response with conversation history as context
+   Γöé
+   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Tier 3: INTERNET SEARCH (if Tier 2 confidence < 0.7)
+   Γöé   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ SerpAPIService.search("Python error handling")
+   Γöé   ΓööΓöÇΓöÇ Results auto-ingested into VectorDB for future queries
+   Γöé
+   ΓööΓöÇΓöÇ Tier 4: USER CONTEXT (if confidence still low)
+       ΓööΓöÇΓöÇ Returns knowledge gap request to user
+   Γöé
+7. RESPONSE ASSEMBLY:
+   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Build RAG prompt with retrieved chunks as context
+   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ LLM generates final response
+   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Save assistant message to ChatHistory
+   ΓööΓöÇΓöÇ Genesis Key: key_type=ai_response, what="RAG retrieval: 3 chunks"
+   Γöé
+8. _call() COMPLETION:
+   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Records latency
+   Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Creates Genesis Key: key_type=api_request, what="brain/chat/send"
+   ΓööΓöÇΓöÇ Returns BrainResponse(ok=true, data={response, chunks, model}, latency_ms=450)
+   Γöé
+9. RESPONSE TO CLIENT:
+   ΓööΓöÇΓöÇ HTTP 200 with BrainResponse JSON
+```
+
