+### Local Vault
+
+`core/security.py` ΓÇö encrypted vault at `data/.vault.enc`:
+- Encrypted with Fernet using `GRACE_MASTER_KEY` env var
+- API: `store_secret()`, `get_secret()`, `rotate_key()`
+- No HashiCorp Vault integration
