+## 39. Frontend State Management
+
+### Zustand Stores
+
+| Store | Persisted? | Key State |
+|-------|-----------|-----------|
+| `usePreferencesStore` | Yes (`grace-preferences`) | Theme, sidebar, font, shortcuts |
