+### Data Sync
+
+- **HTTP polling only** ΓÇö no WebSocket or SSE for state sync
+- `brainCall(domain, action, payload)` ΓåÆ `fetch("POST /brain/{domain}")`
+- `useConnectionStatus` polls `/api/connections/status` every **30 seconds**
+- Chat messages are fetched on demand, not pushed
